  "description": "A nighttime long exposure photograph captures a vibrant fireworks display over a cityscape and a long bridge. The fireworks explode in a brilliant array of colors \u2013 red, white, blue, and gold \u2013 creating a stunning spectacle against the dark sky. Below, the city skyline is illuminated with countless lights, forming a dense urban landscape. A large bridge, with a glowing white railing and support structures, stretches across the dark water in the foreground, adding a sense of scale and depth. The bridge and city appear to be San Francisco. The overall effect is one of celebration and grandeur.",
